commit.message:
PR testsuite/51941 - FAIL g++.dg/debug/dwarf2/nested-3.C on Darwin

gcc/testsuite/

	PR testsuite/51941
	* g++.dg/debug/dwarf2/nested-3.C:  Accept multiple lines between
	the DW_TAG_class_type and DW_AT_name: "Executor".
